snippet.textDisplay: @Rebecca Vocal Athlete: This song REALLy hit me....I’ve been struggling with the same thing for years and just hearing the raw emotion in her voice and still being able to convey that emotion and continue is incredibly impressive; coupled with the lyrics....absolute perfection!! ❤️ I am so happy to see Demi back on stage again! This song means so much to me and I feel blessed to have heard it. As a singer myself I don’t think I’ve heard a song that truly expresses how I’ve been feeling all these years struggling with addiction until I heard THIS! I’ve tried to write songs but I can never get anything out onto paper. This was simply stunning! 💯💯💯
